tags.note: Gate has "private property" and "no trespassing" signs on it, but there's a path that goes around it. This is part of the N 157th St right of way, so I'm uncertain about the legal standing of the signs.
The lights by the signs flash rapidly if the button is pressed. The overhead lights always flash slowly.
This section of trail is NOT part of the Interurban Trail.

tags.description: Overgrown. Difficult to pass due to blackberry thorns.

tags.note: 5' public pedestrian access easement per King County Recording #20131126900011
